'''沃尔沃卡车公司'''（{{lang-sv|Volvo Lastvagnar}}，{{lang-en|Volvo Trucks Corporation}}）是位于[[瑞典|瑞典]][[哥德堡|哥德堡]]的全球[[卡车|卡车]]制造商，品牌标志为VOLVO，由[[沃尔沃集团|AB沃尔沃]]擁有。在2016年，它是全球第二大重型卡车制造商。<ref name="AR2016">{{cite web | url=https://www.volvogroup.com/content/dam/volvo/volvo-group/markets/global/en-en/investors/reports-and-presentations/annual-reports/annual-and-sustainability-report-2016.pdf | title=The Volvo Group Annual And Sustainability Report 2016 | year=2016 | pages=8, 81, 88, 89 | format=PDF | language=en | publisher=Volvo Group | access-date=2020-09-26 | archive-date=2020-07-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729071523/https://www.volvogroup.com/content/dam/volvo/volvo-group/markets/global/en-en/investors/reports-and-presentations/annual-reports/annual-and-sustainability-report-2016.pdf | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2012年，沃尔沃集团重新組織，沃尔沃卡车從此不再是獨立公司，並與包括[[雷諾卡車|雷諾卡車]]、[[麥克貨車|麥克貨車]]、[[UD卡車|UD卡車]]在內的沃尔沃集团卡車公司合併。<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.fleetowner.com/fleet-management/article/21680593/volvo-group-reorganizes-global-truck-business | title=Volvo Group reorganizes global truck business | language=en | publisher=FleetOwner | date=2011-10-04 | accessdate=2020-09-26 | archive-date=2020-06-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200622030720/https://www.fleetowner.com/fleet-management/article/21680593/volvo-group-reorganizes-global-truck-business | dead-url=no }}</ref>

